
Prerequisites
=============
nodejs nodejs-legacy
npm
mongodb
$ npm install -g grunt-cli
$ npm install -g bower

Installation
============
Clone sources from github: git clone
$ cd checkbook   (the directory with this README and a Makefile)
$ make setup
$ cd loopback
$ npm install

Running
=======
window 1: make mongod
Wait for server to start.
window 2: cd loopback; node .
Wait for server to start.
window 3: make grunt

